          <title>
            <string language="sl">Mlada praprot</string>
            <string language="en">Baby fern</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Babyfarn</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Fougère de bébé</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Fern do bebê</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Fern del bambino</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Φτέρη μωρών</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Fern del bebé</string>
          </title>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Mlada praprot je svetlo zelena in konice so zvite v polža.</string>
            <string language="en">Baby fern is light green and tips of the leafs (frond) are tight spiral called a crozier or fiddlehead.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">praprot</string>
            <string language="en">fern</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">rastlina</string>
            <string language="en">plant</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Babyfarn ist hellgrün und Spitzen von treibt 
(Wedel) sind die feste Spirale Blätter, die ein crozier 
genannt werden oder fiddlehead.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La fougère de bébé est vert clair et les 
extrémités du pousse des feuilles (fronde) sont spirale serrée 
appelée un crozier ou fiddlehead.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O fern do bebê é verde claro e as pontas do 
folheiam (frond) são espiral apertada chamada um mais crozier ou 
fiddlehead.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Il fern del bambino è verde chiaro e le punte 
del frondeggia (frond) sono spirale stretta chiamata un più crozier o
fiddlehead.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Η φτέρη μωρών είναι ανοικτό πράσινο και οι άκρες 
βγάζουν φύλλα (φύλλο) είναι σφιχτή σπείρα αποκαλούμενη pjo' 
θροζηερ ή fiddlehead.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El fern del bebé es verde ligero y las 
extremidades del hojean (frond) son espiral apretado llamado un ma's 
crozier o fiddlehead.</string>
          </description>
